    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ready to build the ultimate shopping empire? Dive into the most addictive mall management game where you’re the boss!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179830/extras/df5413ac8c267f3010c9c86006d90d33.poster.avif?t=1744990334\" width=618 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179830/extras/df5413ac8c267f3010c9c86006d90d33.webm?t=1744990334\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179830/extras/df5413ac8c267f3010c9c86006d90d33.mp4?t=1744990334\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the world of retail empire-building with the ultimate shopping center simulation game! From the very first brick to the bustling crowds, you'll have full control over creating your dream shopping mall. Start by designing and decorating your premises, making each space uniquely attractive to potential tenants. With endless customization options, your creativity is the limit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179830/extras/18011b1cf169ea2261f2b3b16c7a9272.poster.avif?t=1744990334\" width=618 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179830/extras/18011b1cf169ea2261f2b3b16c7a9272.webm?t=1744990334\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179830/extras/18011b1cf169ea2261f2b3b16c7a9272.mp4?t=1744990334\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Attract a diverse range of tenants, from boutique shops to major brands, each with their own needs and demands. Your management skills will be put to the test as you negotiate deals, set rental rates, and keep your tenants happy. But it doesn’t stop there — keeping customers satisfied is key to your success. Monitor their needs, adjust your mall’s offerings, and create an environment that keeps the crowds coming back.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179830/extras/1e04d6d96fbd4ca725124c01aaeed29f.poster.avif?t=1744990334\" width=618 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179830/extras/1e04d6d96fbd4ca725124c01aaeed29f.webm?t=1744990334\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179830/extras/1e04d6d96fbd4ca725124c01aaeed29f.mp4?t=1744990334\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As your shopping center thrives, so will your profits. Reinvest your earnings to expand, add new features, and improve your services. With every decision you make, your shopping center will grow, and so will your reputation. Compete to become the most successful tycoon in the industry!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179830/extras/b1ebaadf1aa59986871ea2e176d313fa.poster.avif?t=1744990334\" width=618 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179830/extras/b1ebaadf1aa59986871ea2e176d313fa.webm?t=1744990334\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179830/extras/b1ebaadf1aa59986871ea2e176d313fa.mp4?t=1744990334\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you up for the challenge? Start now and become the ultimate shopping center tycoon!</p>",
